QuestData.Title: A Visit With Maybell
QuestData.Description: You seem like the helpful type, $n. How about doing an old man a favor?$B$BThe last time I was over at the Maclure Vineyards I overheard Maybell crying in her cottage. Would you be so kind as to go check up on her? I'm a little worried.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Maybell Maclure at the Maclure Vineyards in Elwynn Forest.
